{"tid":228301,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"想上ff，影景多。求分析","createTime":"2017-05-03T19:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T18:49:41.000Z","uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bcae7929412421466bf6e4a56b484d33db33d24","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T19:06:34.000Z","msg":"小弟上年買左760d kit set 18-135mm<br />\n用左一年，影景多。。係色差同像素方面覺得不夠滿足。所以想換新<br />\n我睇中左支廣角f4L is Usm 16-35mm<br />\n網上啲人話上2.8會更好，又有朋友講f4 is防震開1/2秒都好正好清<br />\n機的話打算等6d mark2<br />\n請各位大大幫我分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c530850185ca1381267d9dff5895cb6ed8cc6bd6","tid":228301,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T19:19:23.000Z","msg":"2.8 同 4 當然 2.8 好啲㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你銀包夠錢買咪好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係只係講經"},{"pid":"defa9129f7d53e40a85000fa843669e365020eb4","tid":228301,"uid":63009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T19:36:57.000Z","msg":"幾點呀大佬..？<br />\n15分鐘冇人回你就開多次post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2668b86b728c180f422909dbbb0a106422c8c708","tid":228301,"uid":23332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T19:50:27.000Z","msg":"760d 已經24mp都唔夠？ 你要咁大黎做咩？<br />\n色差問題？可唔可以解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n2.8點都好過4，但你有幾多budget 先？<br />\n聽你咁好似無限咁"},{"pid":"33d0027407befafa36ad6c65867b9791326b89ed","tid":228301,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T20:04:46.000Z","msg":"分析乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd6f7b1f86b5e8be1cde3906aa0b605d4036b2d","tid":228301,"uid":74211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:45:50.000Z","msg":"色差像素唔比好太多<br />\n760d又唔係舊機<br />\n不如睇清楚ff同aspc有咩分別先"},{"pid":"969aae07e4b1ae2096b7032f5ba97a7d1ae9dbb7","tid":228301,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:49:22.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\nA7R2 / D810<br />\n其他收皮"},{"pid":"001da80905f67c527ae1e6977bccad5112c8ac2c","tid":228301,"uid":47322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:56:08.000Z","msg":"講影景推d810<br />\n<br />\n不過老老實實你冇技術又唔執相 <br />\n俾部d5你都係垃圾啦"},{"pid":"c6a2f6a1cfab79fa443010bbb99810bf2585868c","tid":228301,"uid":28245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"分析完 你都係戇鳩仔架啦 唔好強姦d機機"},{"pid":"74e73ffb62ed30901c823aa2bf8d1483865e93d7","tid":228301,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"像素唔夠<br />\n商業相阿？"},{"pid":"458e420401081b68fe2620effb5f455e557cbd8c","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2.8 同 4 當然 2.8 好啲㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你銀包夠錢買咪好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係只係講經</blockquote><br />\n明白，咁我都係打算買一支。2.8都可以買係蓄多陣錢"},{"pid":"2efc0ce03fcd691a7d67fc263b1f8750213439f6","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾點呀大佬..？<br />\n15分鐘冇人回你就開多次post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係見f5都無post。以為bug左再開"},{"pid":"ea4c39563a0b525e413cf7a1d93c81531dff401e","tid":228301,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:30:33.000Z","msg":"老實講 俾咩機你都死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都唔知自己做緊咩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d80afe30552e9daefead01b94a0a562192d78e","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>760d 已經24mp都唔夠？ 你要咁大黎做咩？<br />\n色差問題？可唔可以解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n2.8點都好過4，但你有幾多budget 先？<br />\n聽你咁好似無限咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能係我之前都手機過相，上載上網（fb ig）又會壓縮左。我覺得都係有啲矇。<br />\n<br />\n色差係睇人地啲相。同樣既位置。但我影岀黎好似好淺色咁。<br />\n<br />\n我預2萬內，因為影景多。所以覺得買支廣角會適合我多啲。係2.8同4有啲難簡。4個防手震岩我唔用三腳架既人。2.8個光圈又正啲。。好難簡"},{"pid":"fb00d05e0c21c400697035d3e06240366aa3fd2a","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>色差像素唔比好太多<br />\n760d又唔係舊機<br />\n不如睇清楚ff同aspc有咩分別先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以我所知係，影岀黎apsc比ff影既景無咁廣。X1.6既大細。仲有電可以用耐啲。像素高啲。配ff鏡 感光又正啲咁。不過會重好多"},{"pid":"6237f26b19b545f4f238acc2c417202f512c9bc2","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:36:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好簡單<br />\nA7R2 / D810<br />\n其他收皮</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n感謝推介。我再去睇資料比較下"},{"pid":"1876a6bdb2728d39d5e05e6ce0dd0823c967210b","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講影景推d810<br />\n<br />\n不過老老實實你冇技術又唔執相 <br />\n俾部d5你都係垃圾啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。。又係既，我都係用ig禁幾下啲光度 清晰就上載相<br />\n<br />\n我會一直練習🙏🏻多謝意見"},{"pid":"1fbbb48ea8ea9725b081c85d81a20a5864dba185","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:39:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>像素唔夠<br />\n商業相阿？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係。淨係放上網同自己睇"},{"pid":"ea814188d97e7d989d0bb8513d1313539e3d80a4","tid":228301,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:49:27.000Z","msg":"6d都不過二千幾萬像素冇乜用，一定係買5dsr,先有升級感，d相會sharp好多，而且5dsr嘅色係特別調校過，靚過5d3同6d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主唔用腳架，影景一定係用有is果支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342d488904979d751509cb9b2c634cd8764c74aa","tid":228301,"uid":63009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T19:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6d都不過二千幾萬像素冇乜用，一定係買5dsr,先有升級感，d相會sharp好多，而且5dsr嘅色係特別調校過，靚過5d3同6d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主唔用腳架，影景一定係用有is果支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要升級就直接出 1DX啦"},{"pid":"8c89a39266b523c5d4410c3baad5666f1331fa49","tid":228301,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T19:26:24.000Z","msg":"老老實實你啲concept錯鬼哂<br />\n換機唔換腦係解決唔到"},{"pid":"083b629b40b89e88826419696ce46707caa567de","tid":228301,"uid":16839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T23:36:13.000Z","msg":"買貴機唔會送技術同知識嫁樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3393bb56badfaf1e9067c6b3d7cc364808f7356","tid":228301,"uid":59780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T00:05:06.000Z","msg":"用緊1635L4, 好夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d26d3c8e8c54b195c525d5a9c4bff7192f1e02","tid":228301,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T00:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>760d 已經24mp都唔夠？ 你要咁大黎做咩？<br />\n色差問題？可唔可以解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n2.8點都好過4，但你有幾多budget 先？<br />\n聽你咁好似無限咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能係我之前都手機過相，上載上網（fb ig）又會壓縮左。我覺得都係有啲矇。<br />\n<br />\n色差係睇人地啲相。同樣既位置。但我影岀黎好似好淺色咁。<br />\n<br />\n我預2萬內，因為影景多。所以覺得買支廣角會適合我多啲。係2.8同4有啲難簡。4個防手震岩我唔用三腳架既人。2.8個光圈又正啲。。好難簡</blockquote><br />\n你不如睇曬成本manual先"},{"pid":"0668ababf250515ec286ee278c31f5a4bc59bbb2","tid":228301,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T00:49:22.000Z","msg":"D750啦"},{"pid":"b82d671a5b7ceb5ab57baa9d599043af05c5d63b","tid":228301,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T01:04:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>色差像素唔比好太多<br />\n760d又唔係舊機<br />\n不如睇清楚ff同aspc有咩分別先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以我所知係，影岀黎apsc比ff影既景無咁廣。X1.6既大細。仲有電可以用耐啲。像素高啲。配ff鏡 感光又正啲咁。不過會重好多</blockquote><br />\nCanon枝 10-22一樣做到差唔多視角。像素高冇乜撚用（而且高果少少），你曬做廣告poster定大大幅結婚相。日頭冇is 問題不大，夜景多數落腳架，除非你經常手持夜拍"},{"pid":"fce91f00a1f217417daa643601bd2f2f7cb0b57d","tid":228301,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T01:35:30.000Z","msg":"屌，我用緊12mp你叫我情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5571f8b661357431c55cae1c49ff947dd95d8629","tid":228301,"uid":85046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T03:04:01.000Z","msg":"就咁紙上談兵冇乜用<br />\n樓主應該貼d作品出黎俾大家分析下邊部機岩樓主"},{"pid":"bca5f84a524b13bd297aecdacd37db8243bbd703","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6d都不過二千幾萬像素冇乜用，一定係買5dsr,先有升級感，d相會sharp好多，而且5dsr嘅色係特別調校過，靚過5d3同6d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主唔用腳架，影景一定係用有is果支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝意見👍🏻"},{"pid":"8cd3dda6c7eacc2a685b373388fc8283a3e15817","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老實實你啲concept錯鬼哂<br />\n換機唔換腦係解決唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你無錯，我係新手。"},{"pid":"03d3fc4cd1636c3cd76fbf1c1a4e0aa2b0fc86a5","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買貴機唔會送技術同知識嫁樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明，我有練習。都會成日睇網上教學。"},{"pid":"eaf838b60021ccde1cb4196bf090e47e6b692a35","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊1635L4, 好夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝意見"},{"pid":"445460718e0dee1cfc46fedfae05f8af87817836","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁紙上談兵冇乜用<br />\n樓主應該貼d作品出黎俾大家分析下邊部機岩樓主</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h2eY429.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh2eY429.jpg&h=c540075a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/121628_4ff49ece8646bce119c4a3a81858c266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F121628_4ff49ece8646bce119c4a3a81858c266.jpg&h=c1297d33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/121629_2ae7a62bf04e15090d7191c7f968fb88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F121629_2ae7a62bf04e15090d7191c7f968fb88.jpg&h=dc655019&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/121629_04d27320c2e9a90805a446c804071507.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F121629_04d27320c2e9a90805a446c804071507.jpg&h=7bf3208a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b41f80bf2b23fa6a059ff16f28bac5b0545fb0e","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:24:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>色差像素唔比好太多<br />\n760d又唔係舊機<br />\n不如睇清楚ff同aspc有咩分別先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以我所知係，影岀黎apsc比ff影既景無咁廣。X1.6既大細。仲有電可以用耐啲。像素高啲。配ff鏡 感光又正啲咁。不過會重好多</blockquote><br />\nCanon枝 10-22一樣做到差唔多視角。像素高冇乜撚用（而且高果少少），你曬做廣告poster定大大幅結婚相。日頭冇is 問題不大，夜景多數落腳架，除非你經常手持夜拍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非工作，我有諗過如果唔係工作買ff可能用唔曬。但我想影啲自己鐘意既相，想上ff加強感覺。好多時個景影唔曬。。<br />\n多謝意見"},{"pid":"fcf18c5781830a359dae2ec1148bd73e5e3c593d","tid":228301,"uid":14136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:29:40.000Z","msg":"影景一定要ff機，係喺邊度學？<br />\n無錯，感光上係升級左，但係你呢幾張相轉左用ff機嚟影，又會有咩唔同<br />\n喺距離感上，同樓上講用10-22影出嚟會有咩分別？當然你講質素上，桶狀變形呢啲梗係16-35會好啲嫁<br />\n但係你有無用盡你嘅資源去影想影嘅野？而家你支鏡都未用盡部機<br />\n自己搵支二手10-22返嚟玩下先啦，上ff之前都諗下構圖先啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，我認真左<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 600D + 10-22 使用者"},{"pid":"3bcd99b255f23a1801ed6b8cd91bd59acd0bcb6a","tid":228301,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影景一定要ff機，係喺邊度學？<br />\n無錯，感光上係升級左，但係你呢幾張相轉左用ff機嚟影，又會有咩唔同<br />\n喺距離感上，同樓上講用10-22影出嚟會有咩分別？當然你講質素上，桶狀變形呢啲梗係16-35會好啲嫁<br />\n但係你有無用盡你嘅資源去影想影嘅野？而家你支鏡都未用盡部機<br />\n自己搵支二手10-22返嚟玩下先啦，上ff之前都諗下構圖先啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，我認真左<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 600D + 10-22 使用者</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝意見，我會用盡先再考慮<br />\nE+只係問意見。"},{"pid":"9fbd8f26f70eef7757bdf58fa2c0ecf665e559c1","tid":228301,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>色差像素唔比好太多<br />\n760d又唔係舊機<br />\n不如睇清楚ff同aspc有咩分別先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以我所知係，影岀黎apsc比ff影既景無咁廣。X1.6既大細。仲有電可以用耐啲。像素高啲。配ff鏡 感光又正啲咁。不過會重好多</blockquote><br />\nCanon枝 10-22一樣做到差唔多視角。像素高冇乜撚用（而且高果少少），你曬做廣告poster定大大幅結婚相。日頭冇is 問題不大，夜景多數落腳架，除非你經常手持夜拍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非工作，我有諗過如果唔係工作買ff可能用唔曬。但我想影啲自己鐘意既相，想上ff加強感覺。好多時個景影唔曬。。<br />\n多謝意見</blockquote><br />\n你講緊乜春<br />\n你要wide買支10-22咪得<br />\n<br />\n買機唔送知識架"},{"pid":"28949d3355744958c584529a570d485b01c6dfcf","tid":228301,"uid":23332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>760d 已經24mp都唔夠？ 你要咁大黎做咩？<br />\n色差問題？可唔可以解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n2.8點都好過4，但你有幾多budget 先？<br />\n聽你咁好似無限咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能係我之前都手機過相，上載上網（fb ig）又會壓縮左。我覺得都係有啲矇。<br />\n<br />\n色差係睇人地啲相。同樣既位置。但我影岀黎好似好淺色咁。<br />\n<br />\n我預2萬內，因為影景多。所以覺得買支廣角會適合我多啲。係2.8同4有啲難簡。4個防手震岩我唔用三腳架既人。2.8個光圈又正啲。。好難簡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你影完只係send 去手機之後post上網而唔係入電腦既咁不如你都係算鳩數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要懶又想呃like 不如手機加味精app又可以幫你慳幾萬蚊。<br />\n<br />\n你果啲所謂既色差，機身，鏡頭，天氣，時間，同你個人任何一樣都會影響到，後製亦都幫到你，再唔係不如你睇下白平衡啲setting 先<br />\n<br />\n我係咪太認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd4d72120b8ec80a4bdc8f4b4d426a0bdb6ca18","tid":228301,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:24:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>760d 已經24mp都唔夠？ 你要咁大黎做咩？<br />\n色差問題？可唔可以解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n2.8點都好過4，但你有幾多budget 先？<br />\n聽你咁好似無限咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能係我之前都手機過相，上載上網（fb ig）又會壓縮左。我覺得都係有啲矇。<br />\n<br />\n色差係睇人地啲相。同樣既位置。但我影岀黎好似好淺色咁。<br />\n<br />\n我預2萬內，因為影景多。所以覺得買支廣角會適合我多啲。係2.8同4有啲難簡。4個防手震岩我唔用三腳架既人。2.8個光圈又正啲。。好難簡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你影完只係send 去手機之後post上網而唔係入電腦既咁不如你都係算鳩數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要懶又想呃like 不如手機加味精app又可以幫你慳幾萬蚊。<br />\n<br />\n你果啲所謂既色差，機身，鏡頭，天氣，時間，同你個人任何一樣都會影響到，後製亦都幫到你，再唔係不如你睇下白平衡啲setting 先<br />\n<br />\n我係咪太認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係啊 樓主其實適合買條PS license 之後慢慢執<br />\n買機錢都慳埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5f04af097c3bd2649765ead9714e5130c3e54f","tid":228301,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>色差像素唔比好太多<br />\n760d又唔係舊機<br />\n不如睇清楚ff同aspc有咩分別先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以我所知係，影岀黎apsc比ff影既景無咁廣。X1.6既大細。仲有電可以用耐啲。像素高啲。配ff鏡 感光又正啲咁。不過會重好多</blockquote><br />\nCanon枝 10-22一樣做到差唔多視角。像素高冇乜撚用（而且高果少少），你曬做廣告poster定大大幅結婚相。日頭冇is 問題不大，夜景多數落腳架，除非你經常手持夜拍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非工作，我有諗過如果唔係工作買ff可能用唔曬。但我想影啲自己鐘意既相，想上ff加強感覺。好多時個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">景影唔曬</span>。。<br />\n多謝意見</blockquote><br />\n買部360啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5170a54d090c91e962856b3c589b4a1742ac9033","tid":228301,"uid":8260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"成班都唔對題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難得樓主想買機, 緊幾大都買左先啦, 唔買點討論<br />\n仲有, 當器材升級到最好嘅時候就無藉口話器材不足而影唔到靚相, 咁先有動力練好技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句, 功欲善其事 必先利其器"},{"pid":"7ca737c25c71b2ac2ac6c915a1c1684844c1ef7c","tid":228301,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班都唔對題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難得樓主想買機, 緊幾大都買左先啦, 唔買點討論<br />\n仲有, 當器材升級到最好嘅時候就無藉口話器材不足而影唔到靚相, 咁先有動力練好技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句, 功欲善其事 必先利其器</blockquote><br />\n啱啊 樓主一於買部1d m4啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb94f00a5342f7736ba1be626886ec42f236bb10","tid":228301,"uid":113953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>色差像素唔比好太多<br />\n760d又唔係舊機<br />\n不如睇清楚ff同aspc有咩分別先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以我所知係，影岀黎apsc比ff影既景無咁廣。X1.6既大細。仲有電可以用耐啲。像素高啲。配ff鏡 感光又正啲咁。不過會重好多</blockquote><br />\nCanon枝 10-22一樣做到差唔多視角。像素高冇乜撚用（而且高果少少），你曬做廣告poster定大大幅結婚相。日頭冇is 問題不大，夜景多數落腳架，除非你經常手持夜拍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非工作，我有諗過如果唔係工作買ff可能用唔曬。但我想影啲自己鐘意既相，想上ff加強感覺。好多時個景影唔曬。。<br />\n多謝意見</blockquote><br />\n個人意見<br />\n影景忌貪"},{"pid":"3af76f1f7f7d9188c20e70664fb5b8aa183c3d52","tid":228301,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成班都唔對題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難得樓主想買機, 緊幾大都買左先啦, 唔買點討論<br />\n仲有, 當器材升級到最好嘅時候就無藉口話器材不足而影唔到靚相, 咁先有動力練好技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句, 功欲善其事 必先利其器</blockquote><br />\n啱啊 樓主一於買部1d m4啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過1d m4得16mp 應該唔夠影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如直上phase one xf 100mp<br />\n影景一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3922b5968cf4bc3bca658a50dea82967536393bb","tid":228301,"uid":38317,"like":0,"dislik